OL,5, The UK's six biggest water firms are   
OL,6, facing legal action over claims they   
OL,7, underreported pollution and overcharged
OL,8, customers.                             
OL,10,FSevern Trent is the first in line, with
OL,11,Fclaims against the other firms expected
OL,12,Fin the coming months.                  
OL,14,FA law firm says it could result in     
OL,15,Fcustomers on average receiving #40     
OL,16,Feach, but the process could take years 
OL,17,Fand there is no guarantee of success.  
OL,19,FTrade body Water UK said the           
OL,20,Faccusations were "without merit".      
